{"tid":459510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[十一月五日。突發] 德州教堂發生槍擊事件，起碼27名受害者","createTime":"2017-11-05T20:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T04:55:57.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"a201f1cbe9e95fd62a1abb76f3130414a662751e","tid":459510,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T20:02:08.000Z","msg":"咁大獲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BREAKING: 'At least 27 people killed' at a Texas church and multiple people injured - including a two-year-old child - after a gunman in full combat dress opens fire during the service</span><br />\n<br />\n&bull;At least 27 people were shot by a gunman who opened fire just before 11.30am<br />\n&bull;The shooting occurred at the First Baptist Church of Sutherland Springs in Texas <br />\n&bull;A witness said among those who were shot in the attack was a two-year-old child<br />\n&bull;Another witness said a man 'in full gear' walked into the church and opened fire<br />\n&bull;Police confirmed that the gunman is dead and there is no longer a threat in area  <br />\n&bull;Victims were transported to a local hospital and it's unclear if any are deceased <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/05/19/460CF61D00000578-5052163-image-a-80_1509910006766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F19%2F460CF61D00000578-5052163-image-a-80_1509910006766.jpg&h=b4a82062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n At least 27 people have been shot inside a Texas church after a gunman opened fire during the Sunday morning service at the First Baptist Church of Sutherland Springs (pictured)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/05/19/460D1EC300000578-5052163-image-a-79_1509909995986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F19%2F460D1EC300000578-5052163-image-a-79_1509909995986.jpg&h=0e2f3efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The shooting happened at the First Baptist Church of Sutherland Springs, where around 50 people usually attend service, according to local reports<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/05/19/460C57FC00000578-5052163-image-a-67_1509908626240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F19%2F460C57FC00000578-5052163-image-a-67_1509908626240.jpg&h=a91937f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  Sheriff Joe Tackitt confirmed that there are 'multiple casualties and fatalities'. Pictured is the church where the incident took place Sunday morning<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/05/19/460D1ECB00000578-5052163-image-a-78_1509909989262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F19%2F460D1ECB00000578-5052163-image-a-78_1509909989262.jpg&h=ce559cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Witnesses said a man 'in full gear' walked inside the church and opened fire just before 11.30am<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/11/05/18/460C4ABF00000578-0-image-a-49_1509907974955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F18%2F460C4ABF00000578-0-image-a-49_1509907974955.jpg&h=9ca62fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Police (pictured) could not give an exact number of victims shot in the attack, but witnesses said as many as 20 shots were fired<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5052163/Up-16-shot-Texas-church-gunman-opens-fire.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5052163%2FUp-16-shot-Texas-church-gunman-opens-fire.html&d=wdibREn%2B18OlSkWxh8ewnxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a0390a2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5052163/Up-16-shot-Texas-church-gunman-opens-fire.html</a>"},{